OL,3,CSix people, including teenager,
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of murder as
OL,5,Cvictim named
OL,7,FSix people have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder after a man was
OL,9,Ffound stabbed to death in Lewisham.
OL,11,FKamahl, 31, died at the scene after
OL,12,Femergency services responded to
OL,13,Freports of a man with knife injuries
OL,14,Fin Westow Hill, Crystal Palace, on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,17,FA 21-year-old man was arrested on
OL,18,FMonday, 22 June and another man, aged
OL,19,F23, was arrested on Tuesday, 23 June.
OL,20,FThey remain in custody.
