OL,3,CSix people, including teenager,
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of murder as
OL,5,Cvictim named
OL,7,FThe four others include ` a 17-year-
OL,8,Fold boy and three men aged 19, 30 and
OL,9,F45 ` who were also detained on Sunday,.
OL,11,FThey have been released on bail
OL,12,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Sarah Lee
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,16,FKamahl's family and friends as they
OL,17,Fcome to terms with this tragic loss.
OL,19,F"There is no place for knife crime on
OL,20,Four streets.
