OL,3,CSix people, including teenager,
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of murder as
OL,5,Cvictim named
OL,7,F"Our detectives continue to work at
OL,8,Fpace and remain committed to
OL,9,Fapprehending those responsible for
OL,10,Ftaking Kamahl away from his loved ones.
OL,12,F"We have already made significant
OL,13,Farrests and are closing in on
OL,14,Foutstanding suspects.
OL,16,F"Anyone with information that may
OL,17,Fassist our investigation is urged to
OL,18,Fspeak to us as a matter of urgency."
